{
  "captions": [
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>- We have a problem.</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:00:26.480"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>You see, in this time\nbefore memory existed,</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:00:29.079"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>out of nothing...</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:00:38.880"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>a universe was created so big, so massive,</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:00:46.800"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>it is impossible to comprehend\nin any meaningful way.</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:00:52.719"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>But in one small corner of\nthat vast, vast universe,</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:00:57.480"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>through pure chance and the\ngreat infiniteness of time,</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:01:04.039"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>a proliferation of life emerged,</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:01:09.519"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>life that would eventually become us.</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:01:13.199"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>If you think about it,</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:01:20.679"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>from the birth of that first star</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:01:22.880"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>when everything that has ever existed</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:01:25.679"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>or will ever exist emerged, to now,</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:01:28.800"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>the probability of us\nexisting at all is unlikely.</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:01:32.840"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>Ridiculous, even.</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:01:38.920"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>But here we are.</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:01:41.320"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>Me and you.</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:01:43.159"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>And, that makes us all pretty special</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:01:45.280"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>in our own unique way.</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:01:48.519"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>For most of our existence,</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:01:54.639"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>even if we knew very well the act</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:01:57.199"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>that led to the development of life,</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:01:59.840"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>we knew little detail of\nexactly how we were created.</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:02:03.840"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>Yet a mother</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:02:10.000"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>could still feel the\nflutter of new life inside,</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:02:10.960"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>the changes in ones body,\nthe growing bump to know</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:02:15.880"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>that the potential of\nlife existed within them.</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:02:21.039"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>And, when this bump grew enough,</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:02:26.280"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>new life is born.</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:02:30.480"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>Life fraught with the\nresponsibility of its dependency,</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:02:36.039"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>of untold challenges, and reward.</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:02:41.679"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>And, oh, how much reward it can bring.</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:02:45.400"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>Indescribable joy and an\nunspeakable bond that...</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:02:50.920"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>that... is almost beyond\nour simple understanding.</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:02:56.440"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>For some, it can be one of\nthe greatest achievements</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:03:01.960"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>we can ever make.</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:03:06.599"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>But from the darkness of this unknown</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:03:14.840"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>both natural curiosity and a\nburning desire for knowledge</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:03:18.400"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>led us to light..</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:03:23.960"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>In the blink of an eye</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:03:26.719"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>we leapt from measuring the size of a bump</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:03:28.199"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>to looking within it.</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:03:31.920"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>Scans revealed life as it exists here,</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:03:34.159"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>the cord, the sac, a tiny waving hand,</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:03:40.480"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>the beating of their heart.</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:03:46.440"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>We recorded information on each</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:03:49.960"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>and every little growing life we could.</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:03:54.119"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>And then we learnt to do more than look.</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:03:59.079"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>We discovered the code of life itself.</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:04:04.679"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>DNA, Deoxyribonucleic acid, they call it.</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:04:10.280"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>It's not important to\nknow exactly what it is,</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:04:18.159"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>or to worry about the\ncoding, non-coding dilemma.</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:04:22.159"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>All you need to know is, it is the code,</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:04:27.360"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>born of when your father's\nsperm met your mother's egg,</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:04:31.400"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>that instructed every gene, every cell,</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:04:36.199"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>tissue, skin cell,</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:04:41.000"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>every ounce of blood,\nevery organ to be created,</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:04:44.079"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>so you could become you.</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:04:49.719"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>Over time, we researched and\nexplored what DNA could do,</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:04:59.960"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>finally laying out the human genome,</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:05:06.519"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>the entire set of\ninstructions of our being,</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:05:10.280"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>a genetic map of ourselves.</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:05:15.639"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>Through this prism, the\nvery knowledge of genetics</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:05:21.639"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>began to shape how we think and understand</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:05:25.320"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>all living beings.</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:05:30.679"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>In no time at all, a sample of your hair,</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:05:35.880"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>or a swab of your mouth\ncould reveal your history,</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:05:40.320"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>understand your present,\nand predict your future.</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:05:44.960"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>We know genetics is not\nall there is, far from it,</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:05:51.119"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>but they are the core,\nthe building blocks,</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:05:56.719"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>the foundation of life that\nshape and evolve with us.</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:06:00.280"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>Soon enough we learnt to\nshape those very foundations,</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:06:10.880"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>to control what once we could not.</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:06:15.840"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>And, these new abilities\nin genetic engineering,</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:06:20.599"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>makes every action, every inaction</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:06:25.360"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>in the genetic development\nof our children a choice.</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:06:29.679"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>A power both awesome and terrifying,</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:06:36.000"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>the moral dilemmas that\narise from this power</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:06:40.760"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>may be the biggest\nhumanity has ever faced.</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:06:45.199"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>That is why today</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:06:51.920"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>I need to know what role\ngenetic engineering will play</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:06:54.199"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>in the development of our unborn children.</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:06:59.159"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>For when the fate of humanity is at sake..</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:07:04.920"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>There can be greater\nresponsibility, no greater urgency,</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:07:08.519"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>to the answers we seek.</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:07:15.280"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>For us to find the true\nanswers to these dilemmas,</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:07:20.559"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>I need to ask you to place yourself</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:07:25.280"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>in the role of an expectant parent.</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:07:28.000"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>Think of this as a test\nof your imagination,</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:07:31.719"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>a role play, if you like.</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:07:36.199"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>So, lets go on this journey together.</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:07:40.320"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>Close your eyes if you will</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:07:43.800"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>and lets imagine what it is</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:07:46.119"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>to be this expectant parent.</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:07:48.599"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>Imagine that first\npregnancy test turning blue,</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:07:57.880"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>or the confirmation of successful IVF,</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:08:03.119"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>the ecstasy of knowing,</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:08:07.320"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>and the trepidation of\nhaving created a new life,</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:08:09.800"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>and the practicality of what that life</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:08:14.159"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>may mean to your every day.</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:08:17.880"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>Imagine yourself in the heyday\nof your life or maybe not;</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:08:22.640"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>prepared most likely not,</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:08:27.439"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>because we never are\nbut still in a position</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:08:30.680"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>to bring new life into this world.</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:08:35.800"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>If you really cannot get there,</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:08:39.560"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>maybe take the role of a supportive friend</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:08:42.079"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>or family member...</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:08:45.119"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>Are we there?</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:08:49.239"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>Okay, hold that thought in your mind</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:08:52.359"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>and open your eyes, if you will.</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:08:55.960"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>Don't lose that thought.</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:09:00.880"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>Keep holding.</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:09:03.119"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>Here are your fragile new lives.</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:09:06.399"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>Each one an individual,\nlinked to the decisions you,</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:09:09.319"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>and you alone make.</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:09:12.319"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>Each one a child to be, a\nchild cherished and wanted.</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:09:17.199"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>Yearned and planned for.</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:09:22.920"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>A parent to them you wish...\nwish desperately to be.</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:09:25.279"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>And, I want to ask if for\nthis fragile little life,</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:09:32.239"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>we are imagining bringing into the world</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:09:38.359"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>if would you consider changing it?</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:09:42.000"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>Changing the genetic makeup</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:09:46.600"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>that it was originally destined to have?</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:09:49.079"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>For in a time before now,\nour ignorance, our inability,</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:09:53.399"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>protected us from the questions</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:09:59.399"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>of altering our own species...</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:10:01.680"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>But not now and not for you\nbecause it is these questions,</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:10:05.199"
    },
    {
      "duration": 0,
      "content": "<b>of altering our own species</b>",
      "startOfParagraph": null,
      "startTime": "00:10:10.640"
    },
